title: Trapped
resume:
Trapped is a documentary television series that premiered on November 7, 2007 on the National Geographic Channel. Produced in association with the National Geographic Channel and Cineflix, the program examines various actual incidents or disasters in which victims were trapped on the site.
As of 12 December 2007, six episodes have been aired.
